
********************************************************************************

                           RANLUX --- Version 3.4

********************************************************************************


Documentation
-------------

doc/guide.pdf    User's guide for the programs in this directory.

doc/notes.pdf    Description of the underlying algorithms.


Programs
--------

ranlxd.c         Double-precision generator and associated utility programs.

ranlxs.c         Single-precision generator and associated utility programs.

ranlux_common.c  Basic functions used in ranlxd.c and ranlxs.c.

testlx.c         Main program that checks whether the generators work properly
                 on the chosen machine and with the chosen compiler options.

timelx.c         Main program that measures the processor time required per
                 generated random number.

The functions in ranlux_common.c are not intended to be used by any programs
other than those in ranlxd.c and ranlxs.c


Include file
------------

ranlux.h       Function allusions (prototypes) of the externally accessible
               functions in the modules ranlxd.c and ranlxs.c.

********************************************************************************
